{"tid":2157252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Shake Shack北京開店 市民:喜歡豆漿油條不代表不喜歡漢堡奶昔","createTime":"2020-08-15T02:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T04:25:37.000Z","uid":49776,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3aeaf88124a4f2c9fcbcfe18b03108f3ab6a1d37","tid":2157252,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200812/s00004/d0417d53920147af9c512982f2c02fc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200812%2Fs00004%2Fd0417d53920147af9c512982f2c02fc5.jpg&h=81c972ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200812/s00004/d081aa4da795ce831ee79209c508dbcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200812%2Fs00004%2Fd081aa4da795ce831ee79209c508dbcb.jpg&h=9a814594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國紐約漢堡品牌Shake Shack北京首家分店今日（12日）中午在三里屯開幕，數百名顧客清晨起冒雨排隊嘗鮮。<br />\n<br />\n天文台預報今日北京將有暴雨，但沒有熄滅年輕人「打卡」的熱情。排隊市民陳先生稱，他很關注Shake Shack在北京的銷售商品，「之前在上海他們會銷售符合上海文化的奶昔。這次很想知道他們會銷售什麼樣的北京文化」。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生說，現在中美兩國關係異常緊張，但是對普通百姓而言，更需要的是和平的生活，中國百姓喜歡豆漿和油條，不代表不喜歡漢堡和奶昔。「美國的漢堡品牌在北京銷售北京的文化產品，這是一種文化的融合與認同。為什麼非要對立呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20200812/s00004/1597219118979/shake-shack%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%97-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BE%E5%A7%93%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E8%B1%86%E6%BC%BF%E6%B2%B9%E6%A2%9D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E6%BC%A2%E5%A0%A1%E5%A5%B6%E6%98%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20200812%2Fs00004%2F1597219118979%2Fshake-shack%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%25A7%2593%25E5%2596%259C%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25B1%2586%25E6%25BC%25BF%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2596%259C%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E6%2598%2594&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8XvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=11ab6c35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20200812%2Fs00004%2F1597219118979%2Fshake-shack%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%25A7%2593%25E5%2596%259C%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25B1%2586%25E6%25BC%25BF%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2596%259C%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E6%2598%2594&h=f7005dac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20200812/s00004/1597219118979/shake-shack%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%97-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BE%E5%A7%93%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E8%B1%86%E6%BC%BF%E6%B2%B9%E6%A2%9D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E6%BC%A2%E5%A0%A1%E5%A5%B6%E6%98%94</a></span>"},{"pid":"6197a2d2e0c6fb964af180ab4ec2c0f283eb11f4","tid":2157252,"uid":286897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cde2de07d5123c6cebea02b29625e4cce23a8d20","tid":2157252,"uid":49776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6197a2d2e0c6fb964af180ab4ec2c0f283eb11f4","tid":2157252,"uid":286897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"反美是工作"},{"pid":"4e30ded8ec24e32391d3f03f543f994f872c463f","tid":2157252,"uid":314136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"食窮美資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><